name: DOGAMI
description: DOGAMÍ is a mass-market Web3 entertainment company focused on creating experiences based on NFTs. DOGAMÍ’s experiences are unlocked by Dogamí NFTs: mystical 3D dog avatars imbued with spiritual powers. They act as keys to the DOGAMÍ ecosystem to offer a new level of interactivity, ownership, and value. You must train them to unlock their full potential. Leveraging their recent success, Dogamí has expanded its ecosystem to support EVM and now provides a seamless multichain experience across Ethereum, Polygon, and Tezos.
